?_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=pAVAcIVWgCMQ7kNvgFvUvzo&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYAN2L5UnHzGMJySUvKN6Ip494m3RgbU2wo7Jw2xDISepg&oe=675193B5"}], "video_trailer": null, "video_trailer_thumbnail": {"file_name": "PUB_Demeo1_Landscape_2560x1440.png", "id": "3364234113798972", "uri": "https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982595_3364234117132305_4261357680553079905_n.png?_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=66GD1NmIhtoQ7kNvgEnSjkG&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYCXKsA2xw7lM8kTjXDWeGKoSjZoFP-CmGGLXCggRnXccQ&oe=67519817"}, "display_name": "Demeo Battles", "keywords": ["tactics", "strategy", "tabletop", "pvp", "battle"], "long_description": "# Fast-Paced Tactical PvP Battles\nDemeo Battles brings **intense, turn-based strategy** to life as you battle opponents in grid-based combat across dynamic maps. Assemble your team of champions and chaotic creatures for quick, thrilling matches.\n\n\u200e\n\n# Assemble Your Ultimate Team\nChoose two champions from 7 distinct classes \u2013 hunter, sorcerer, assassin, guardian, bard, warlock or barbarian \u2013 each with their own powers and playstyle. Combine magic, ranged, and melee to create unstoppable synergies.\n\n\u200e\n\n# Key Features:\n- **Speedy Matched** \u2013 Engage in quick, intense matches \u2013 each lasting under 20 minutes \u2013 that combine strategy with fast decision-making.\n- **Heroic Teamwork** \u2013 Control two champions or team up with another player to dominate the arena.\n- **Customizable Playstyles** \u2013 Choose from 7 classes, each offering unique gameplay experiences. Pick from over 80 action cards to create a bespoke loadout.\n- **Monstrous Minions** \u2013 Command over 30 chaotic creatures, from cave trolls to giant slimes, all with unique abilities.\n- **Single-Player Challenges** \u2013 Sharpen your skills in 60 tactical challenges.\n- **Ranked Progression** \u2013 Climb the ranks in month-long competitive seasons.\n- **Cross-Play and Mixed Reality** \u2013 Play with friends on any supported device, and experience the game in MR mode.\n\n\u200e\n\n# Welcome to the Arena!\nDemeo Battles takes everything you love about Demeo and ramps up the action for competitive PvP. Prove your strategic mastery in a whole new way!", "short_description": "A fast-paced, turn-based strategy game where quick decisions and teamwork are key! Fight in intense PvP battles with 7 unique hero classes, summon chaotic creatures, and customize your loadout. Play solo, co-op, or compete in multiplayer modes across dynamic, mixed reality maps. With matches lasting under 20 minutes, every second counts in this thrilling tactical experience!"}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://www.resolutiongames.com/privacy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": "https://www.resolutiongames.com/terms-of-use", "publisher_name": "Resolution Games", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "http://demeobattles.com/", "category": "GAMES", "comfort_rating": "COMFORTABLE_FOR_MOST", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "2743326035925534", "context_category": "GAMES"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "275629210202852"}, {"id": "1676485315806614"}, {"id": "821934236779161"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["ACTION", "RPG", "STRATEGY"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "NO_MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en", "zh_CN", "fr", "de", "ja", "ko", "es"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH", "HAND_TRACKING"], "supported_player_modes": ["SITTING", "STANDING"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["MULTI_USER"], "id": "8691438214273651"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-fra5-2.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/38982535_1260959085243515_3543087642505107214_n.png?stp=dst-png_s3